OverwatchTeamUp.WebApplication.TeamCompositionUI --> OverwatchTeamUp.WebApplication.PrototypeData <<Relationship-UmVsYXRpb25zaGlw>> : "Uses fallback team composition data from"
OverwatchTeamUp.WebApplication.HeroBrowser --> OverwatchTeamUp.BackendAPI <<Relationship-UmVsYXRpb25zaGlw>> : "Loads hero summaries directly with fetch\n<size:16>[JSON/HTTPS]</size>"
OverwatchTeamUp.WebApplication.TeamCompositionUI --> OverwatchTeamUp.BackendAPI <<Relationship-UmVsYXRpb25zaGlw>> : "Loads team compositions directly with fetch\n<size:16>[JSON/HTTPS]</size>"
OverwatchTeamUp.WebApplication.AuthenticationUI --> OverwatchTeamUp.BackendAPI <<Relationship-UmVsYXRpb25zaGlw>> : "Registers and signs in directly with fetch\n<size:16>[JSON/HTTPS]</size>"

